3. ITS-2: 17.8-31.1% (23.7% on average), with the most similar being 

Mil. t. tardigradum

from Germany (JF951049.1) (
Michalczyk et al. 2012
) and the least similar being 
Mil. cf. granulatum
from USA (MK681879.1) (
